column5: another good day on my favorite river back in the town i grew up in. love going back. brings back so many memories and i think the fishing has gotten better...  first catch of the day my dog caught a half dead catfish    myself...i got a few rock bass, 4 pickerel (all small ones) and one decent oos smallmouth all fish released to be caught another day.      overall a beautiful day.
how can i make my pics larger and add more? it shows combined they have to be less then 250k. HELP!
with photobucket, and it's free.  you add the insert image to the post with the link to the photobucket img.
